			<div class="excerpt-text">
				<p class="title"><a href="http://allthingsd.com/20111109/a-guide-for-pc-buyers-not-looking-for-a-tablet/">A Guide for PC Buyers Not Looking for a Tablet</a></p>
				<p class="byline">Walt Mossberg in Personal Technology</p>
